query:

  (SELECT id FROM properties WHERE addressLine1 = '6717 Arbor Dr' AND city = 'Miramar' ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1),
  'PROPERTY: 6717 Arbor Dr, Miramar, FL 33023
Single-Family Home | Built 1965 | 3 Bed / 2 Bath | 1,544 sq ft

CURRENT OWNER: Len D. Sumlar
Occupation: Manager, Morgue Bureau Operations, Miami-Dade County Medical Examiner
Owned Since: 2019
Purchase Price: $200,000

CURRENT RESIDENT: Davion Hudson (Age 36)
Phone: (954) 966-0140
Party: Democratic | Voter Registration: Broward County, FL

OTHER RESIDENTS: Frona S. Hudson (Age 63, Phone: 954-986-8378), Dillon Hudson, Donovan Hudson, Daphnee Francois, Fiona Hudson

VALUATION:
• Redfin Estimate: $459,014 ($297/sq ft)
• Homes.com Estimate: $544,857 ($352/sq ft)
• Average: $501,936
• Last Sale (1994): $85,000
• Owner Purchase (2019): $200,000

APPRECIATION:
• 1994 to 2025: +440% to +540% (+$374,000 to $459,000)
• 2019 to 2025: +$301,936 to $344,857 (+151% to +172%)

PROPERTY TAXES:

• Status: Current and Paid

PROBATE STATUS: ❌ No Probate Case

• No deceased owner identified
• No estate complications

CODE VIOLATIONS: ✅ None
• No open violations
• Compliant with all codes

PROPERTY CONDITION:
• Off-market (not for sale)
• Occupied by identified residents
• Well-maintained
• Strong appreciation area',
  '[]'
);
